A–E worker function
runDashboardQualityDashboardVerificationSections_
Active path
runDashboardQualityDashboardVerificationSections_
  -> get active spreadsheet
  -> ensure Dashboard Quality Report sheet
  -> get Format Dashboard sheet

  If Format Dashboard missing:
    -> save Section A failure rows
    -> replace Dashboard Quality section
    -> mark "Format Dashboard missing"
    -> return

  Else:
    -> build section payloads:
       A Global Inputs
       B Sheet Definitions
       C Sheet Headers
       D Column Definitions
       E Sheet Behaviors

    -> for each section:
       -> read previous saved rows
       -> collect current verification rows
       -> compare previous/current rows
       -> save section rows to document properties with deferSheetWrite
       -> mark timing step
       -> if changed, stage section write

    -> if any changed:
       -> replaceDashboardQualitySectionsRows_
    -> else:
       -> mark sheet write skipped
The function builds payloads for Sections A–E and stages changed section writes. 

